data.description: Welcome to 645 Aspen Ln,  presenting a great opportunity to own a home in Spring Hill Acres. This charming residence offers an open living and dining room area with easy access to the deck from the kitchen, creating an ideal indoor-outdoor living experience. The spacious living room is further enhanced by double glass doors that lead out to an inviting lower deck. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, with a bathroom and a master bath featuring a convenient walk-in shower. The lower level is a basement complete with laundry facilities and ample storage space. Outside, you'll be enticed by the beautiful wooded surroundings, featuring a relaxing hot tub in the back and a storage shed perfect for pets or additional storage. This property offers a relaxing and well-rounded lifestyle in Spring Hill Acres – don't miss your chance to make it your own.
